#

Bacon Avocado Burger

25 min
$12.5
800 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten (if using regular buns)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Quick MealComfort FoodAmerican Cuisine

Description

A deliciously juicy burger topped with crispy bacon and creamy avocado, perfect for a satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef (80/20): 1 lb
  • burger buns: 2
  • avocado: 1
  • bacon strips: 4
  • cheddar cheese: 2 slices
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 4 slices
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
  • onion powder: 1/2 tsp
